    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This rather simple technique requires nothing more than a cloak of some form and a basic understanding of shadow arts. Rather than actually become one with shadows, this technique allows the user to use their own shadow in combination with the shadows of their environment to create a fine fabric of shadow to hide their location.<br><br>As long as the user remains in the shadow of an object one size category larger than his / herself, does not move, and concentrates on this technique the user is treated as invisible and obtains all of the benefits (and limitations) of invisibility. Combat of any form disrupts this technique.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Requires:</b> ; Shadow Arts</p>\n<p><b>Material Focus:</b> Any hooded cloak</p>\n",
